Package: unregistry
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight container image registry backed by Docker daemon storage
 unregistry is a lightweight container image registry that stores and serves
 images directly from your Docker daemon's storage.

Package: docker-pussh
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Push Docker images to remote servers over SSH
 docker-pussh lets you push images straight to remote Docker servers over SSH.
 It transfers only the missing layers, making it fast and efficient.
